Package: raspimidihub
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.9), libasound2t64 | libasound2, alsa-utils, avahi-daemon
Recommends: raspimidihub-rosetup
Description: Automatic USB MIDI hub for Raspberry Pi
 RaspiMIDIHub turns a Raspberry Pi into a dedicated, appliance-like USB MIDI
 hub. When powered on, it automatically routes MIDI data between all connected
 USB MIDI devices. Supports hot-plug detection, loop prevention, and multi-port
 devices.
